sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as 任务需求方/节点(客户端)
    participant EK as x/edgeai (MsgServer+Keeper)
    participant PN as x/phonenode
    participant DP as x/depin (PayOutFromPool)
    participant BM as x/bank
    participant TK as x/tokenomics(只读)

    rect rgb(235,245,255)
    note over U,EK: ① 任务发布 → 领取 → 提交结果（attestation 双闸口）
    U->>EK: CreateTask(creator, spec, reward_amount)
    EK->>EK: 写 Task{status=open}
    U->>EK: AssignTask(taskId, nodeAddr)
    EK->>PN: IsAttested(nodeAddr) + HasNode(nodeAddr)
    alt 未 attest / 已领取
        EK-->>U: 拒绝 (ErrNotAttested / ErrAlreadyAssigned)
    else 通过
        EK->>EK: Task{status=assigned, assigned_to=nodeAddr}
    end
    U->>EK: SubmitResult(taskId, executor, proof_root, result_hash)
    EK->>PN: IsAttested(executor) + HasNode(executor)
    EK->>EK: 写 Result{status=pending, attested=true, dispute_until=cur+DisputePeriodBlocks}
    end

    rect rgb(235,255,238)
    note over EK,DP: ② BeginBlock optimistic 自动接受 + 拨付（不 mint）
    EK->>EK: BeginBlockAccept(ctx) 扫描 pending 且 cur>=dispute_until 且无未决 Dispute
    EK->>EK: acceptResult → Result{status=accepted}
    EK->>DP: PayOutFromPool(executor, reward_amount)
    DP->>BM: SendCoinsFromModuleToAccount(depinModule, executor, amt)  // 从生态池切片
    EK--x TK: 绝不调用 MintCoins（minted_supply 不变）
    end

    rect rgb(255,240,235)
    note over U,EK: ③ 争议 → 裁定 → slash / 奖励（复用 B2）
    U->>EK: SubmitDispute(taskId, challenger, reason)
    EK->>PN: IsAttested(challenger)
    EK->>EK: 写 Dispute{status=open}
    U->>EK: ResolveDispute(resolver, taskId, cheated=true)
    EK->>EK: 校验 resolver == Params.ResolverAddress
    alt cheated=true
        EK->>PN: SlashIfBad(executor, "edgeai_cheat", SlashBpsOnCheat)
        EK->>DP: PayOutFromPool(challenger, challengerReward)
    else cheated=false（恶意挑战）
        EK->>PN: SlashIfBad(challenger, "edgeai_false_dispute", SlashBpsOnCheat)
    end
    EK--x TK: 无任何 MintCoins
    end
